::As Persephone lays there calmly, a transparent form sits up slightly. Then, as if struggling to get out, her tranparent form falls back into her body. After a few seconds, Persephone's chest heaves up taking a huge gasping breath, her eyes open wide with blood running hard thorugh each vein. Clasping down on the bed, she pants hard. She looks around at everyone and looks up at Hades. Her eyes pleading and confused:: <br>
<br>
H-hades? whats happened? <p>*~* Persephone...Queen of the Underworld.. Faithful wife to Hades... Princess Goddess of the Spring*~*</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixlordhadesxi>IX Lord Hades XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 256<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/11/03 1:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=74>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The cure...</span><hr size=1> ::Hades watched Persephone, with a completely sangfroid demeanor. On the surface he looked calm, cool, and collected. However, internally, he was worried about her. He did not like to see her in pain at all, but he had to look as though he was in complete control::<br>
<br>
::Hades then walked over and placed his hand on Persephone's forehead. His hand started glowing purple, the same shade that his eyes were glowing, and in doing this, even more of the light in the room seemed to dim away.::<br>
<br>
&quot;Everything will be alright. Very shortly you will be vomitting up blood, but rest asured, it is not your own blood. It is merely poison. Your body needs to get rid of it.&quot;<br>
<br>
::He then maintained his hand on her forehead, making sure that her spirit stayed in harmony with her body. That she would not leave her body again.::<br>
<br>
::Persephone heard in her mind:: ~Do not worry, my love. Everything will fine.~ ::It was Hades communicating to her in her mind:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=persephoneqofu>PersephoneQofU</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 212<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/11/03 11:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=75>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.aishwarya-rai.com/tradi/tash16.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> sorry</span><hr size=1> ::Persephone looks up into Hades' eyes nodding as she hears him. After a few minutes, she turns over and begins to purge the one thing that could actually kill her. A servant dives toward the bed dramatically and puts a large bowl under her mouth just in the knick of time. After a minute, Persephone lies back down on her bed, feeling a bit nauseated, but much better while the servants and physicians leave. She looks up at Hades::<br>
<br>
Oh darling, I'm so sorry that I yelled at you.. <br>
<br>
::She takes his hand off her forehead and cups it over her damp, cold cheek. She then breaks down into hard long sobs:: Lay down and hold me, please! <p>*~* Persephone...Queen of the Underworld.. Faithful wife to Hades... Princess Goddess of the Spring*~*</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=persephoneqofu>PersephoneQofU</A> at: 5/11/03 11:24:22 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixlordhadesxi>IX Lord Hades XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 258<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/11/03 11:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=76>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Still sore</span><hr size=1> ::Hades merely nodded as Persephone apologized to him for snapping at him. Hades allowed her to manipulate his hand by placing it over her cheek. He simply nodded and gave a smile, and then lied beside her as per her request. He wrapped his arms around her and held her close::<br>
<br>
::He whispered quietly into her ear:: <br>
<br>
&quot;I can't stay long though, I have to figure out who has been doing this...but I have some time&quot;<br>
<br>
::Hades managed to stop keep his eyes from glowing purple and allowed the temperature to return to normal. He supressed the fact that he was still sore about when she lashed out at him. He kept that hidden away from everyone, including himself to some extent:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=persephoneqofu>PersephoneQofU</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 213<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/12/03 3:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=77>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Asleep</span><hr size=1> ::Persephone nods as she hears his words and lays her damp head on his chest::<br>
<br>
Oh Hades, I love you so much, more than anyone I've ever known. When I saw you standing outside of your body, I nearly lost my mind. I do not mean to yell, its just that sometimes I become so miserable and I say things that I do not mean. Just hold me here until I fall asleep..please..<br>
<br>
::With that, Persephone closes her eyes and snuggles up to her husband. After a few minutes, tiny, soft snores begin to purr from her sweet lips:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixlordhadesxi>IX Lord Hades XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 264<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/16/03 3:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=78>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Seeking answer</span><hr size=1> ::Hades lied there quietly until Persephone fell asleep. Rather than disturb her by moving, he melded into a shadow and reappeared at the doorway. He blew her a kiss and walked out of the room allowing her to sleep soundly::<br>
<br>
::He then sneered:: &quot;Okay...time for me to find the saboteurs.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=302.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=302.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=302.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=302.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=302.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=78><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=302.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=302.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=302.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=302.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height